                                            <tr>
                                                <td width="340">
                                                <p style="color: rgb(118, 107, 101); padding-bottom: 5px; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13pt; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 18px;">Lots of schools are emailing you today, but only one wants you to start college now. Only one is specifically designed for smart, highly motivated students who are ready to start college after 10th or 11th grade.</p>
                                                <p style="color: rgb(118, 107, 101); padding-bottom: 5px; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13pt; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 18px;">Instead of going back to high school this fall, you could be away at college, taking courses with inspiring professors and classmates who are as motivated as you.</p>
                                                <p style="color: rgb(191, 42, 35); padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13pt; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 18px;"><em class="ItalicString" style="color: rgb(191, 42, 35); font-size: 13pt;">&ldquo;Students aren't here because they were expected to go. They are here because they had the motivation, they love learning, and they want to be challenged.&rdquo; Jameson, soph.</em></p>
                                                </td>
